          <p>Implemented new ‚Üí dev ‚Üí production source lifecycle via Google Sheets control plane.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="week-card">
          <span class="week-num">Week 10</span>
          <h4>Security & Docs</h4>
          <p>Migrated API keys to Secret Manager. Updated cloud architecture diagrams for the full team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="week-card">
          <span class="week-num">Week 11</span>
          <h4>Cloud Functions Automation</h4>
